Recreation and sport play an important part in the lives of the local inhabitants. Some facilities are provided by the Metropolitan Borough of{Calderdale,}whilst others are provided by the local people in the form of{private clubs.}
The{Greetland All Rounders Rugby Club} and the{Greetland Community Centre} provide excellent facilities. There is a beautiful golf course at Norland. These facilities are not simply used for sporting occasions. They are for social occasions as well. The local people use the premises for{discos}and parties for both children and adults.
{Cricket}plays an important part in the lives of the inhabitants. There are many local cricket clubs and local teams.
